/#
   Describes the limits on the size of notional when multiple exercise is allowed.
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.FxMultipleExercise {
  # The minimum amount of notional that can be exercised.
  minimumNotionalAmount : FpML5.reporting.NonNegativeMoney?

  # The maximum amount of notiional that can be exercised.
  maximumNotionalAmount : FpML5.reporting.NonNegativeMoney?

}

minimumNotionalAmount.Doc: The minimum amount of notional that can be exercised.
minimumNotionalAmount.Name: minimumNotionalAmount

maximumNotionalAmount.Doc: The maximum amount of notiional that can be exercised.
maximumNotionalAmount.Name: maximumNotionalAmount
